2008-06-09  Wouter Bolsterlee  <wbolster@svn.gnome.org>

	* libmuine/player-gst.c (player_finalize), (bus_message_cb):

	Removed iterate_cb() function that didn't do anything
	but causing thousands of wakeups per second (according
	to powertop).

2008-02-26  Wouter Bolsterlee  <wbolster@svn.gnome.org>

	* src/PlaylistWindow.cs:

	Bug 518828 – Disambiguate Bacon.VolumeButton from
	Gtk.VolumeButton

2008-02-26  Wouter Bolsterlee  <wbolster@svn.gnome.org>

	* configure.in:
	
	Bug 518829 – Detect FLAC using pkgconfig file instead of header.

