2005-01-10  Tamara Roberson  <tamara.roberson@gmail.com>

	* data/muine.schemas.in:
	* src/AddAlbumWindow.cs:
	* src/AddSongWindow.cs:
	* src/AddWindow.cs:
	* src/AddWindowEntry.cs:
